# Cloudflare + AI (contingency layer)

1. **Authority:** PC/NAS + hub manifests outrank Cloudflare. Edge is optional hosting / emergency read-only — see [docs/Z-CLOUDFLARE-AI-COMMS-PRECAUTIONS.md](docs/Z-CLOUDFLARE-AI-COMMS-PRECAUTIONS.md).
2. **Secrets:** Never commit API tokens, Account ID (unless policy allows in private repo), or Wrangler secrets. Use dashboard + local untracked env.
3. **Ask AI (Cloudflare dashboard):** Navigation hints only — verify against [MONOREPO_GUIDE.md](MONOREPO_GUIDE.md) Phase 7 and [rules/Z_SANCTUARY_SECURITY_POLICY.md](rules/Z_SANCTUARY_SECURITY_POLICY.md).
